# CODEOWNERS — TNG Agent Team Domain Ownership
#
# Maps repository paths to responsible agents for review routing.
# Each line: <path-pattern> <github-user-or-team>
#
# Agent Domain Map:
#   picard   → orchestration, governance, top-level config
#   data     → architecture, design, system patterns
#   geordi   → CI/CD workflows, DevOps automation
#   worf     → security hardening, compliance
#   troi     → testing, QA, user experience
#   crusher  → reliability, health, edge-case coverage
#   barclay  → technical debt, refactoring, code quality
#   guinan   → session journals, ADRs, institutional history
#   obrien   → monitoring, observability, operational config
#   riker    → execution coordination, cross-team tasks
#
# Replace @jambione/<agent> with actual GitHub team names when teams are configured.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Default owner (picard) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                           @jambione

# ── CI/CD Workflows (geordi) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/workflows/                          @jambione/geordi
.github/workflows/ci.yml                   @jambione/geordi
.github/workflows/kb-staleness-check.yml   @jambione/geordi
.github/workflows/adr-workflow.yml         @jambione/geordi @jambione/data

# ── Security Configuration (worf) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/CODEOWNERS                         @jambione/worf @jambione/picard

# ── Agent Definitions (picard + domain owner) ─────────────────────────────────
.github/agents/                            @jambione
.github/agents/picard*.agent.md            @jambione
.github/agents/data.agent.md               @jambione/data
.github/agents/geordi.agent.md             @jambione/geordi
.github/agents/worf.agent.md               @jambione/worf
.github/agents/troi.agent.md               @jambione/troi
.github/agents/crusher.agent.md            @jambione/crusher
.github/agents/riker.agent.md              @jambione/riker
.github/agents/barclay.agent.md            @jambione/barclay
.github/agents/guinan.agent.md             @jambione/guinan
.github/agents/obrien.agent.md             @jambione/obrien

# ── Prompt Templates (picard + requesting domain) ─────────────────────────────
.github/prompts/                           @jambione

# ── Clinerules (mirrors agent ownership) ──────────────────────────────────────
.clinerules/                               @jambione

# ── Knowledge Base (domain specialist per document) ───────────────────────────
knowledge_base/                            @jambione
knowledge_base/documents/index.md          @jambione

# Architecture domain → data
knowledge_base/documents/architecture-*.md            @jambione/data
knowledge_base/documents/system-design-*.md           @jambione/data
knowledge_base/documents/architecture-decision-*.md   @jambione/data @jambione/guinan

# DevOps domain → geordi
knowledge_base/documents/ci-cd-*.md                   @jambione/geordi
knowledge_base/documents/devops-*.md                  @jambione/geordi
knowledge_base/documents/github-actions-*.md          @jambione/geordi

# Security domain → worf
knowledge_base/documents/github-actions-security-*.md @jambione/worf @jambione/geordi

# Testing domain → troi
knowledge_base/documents/best-practices.md            @jambione/troi
knowledge_base/documents/defect-*.md                  @jambione/troi

# Reliability domain → crusher
knowledge_base/documents/incident-*.md                @jambione/crusher

# Technical debt → barclay
knowledge_base/documents/tech-debt-*.md               @jambione/barclay

# Observability → obrien
knowledge_base/documents/monitoring-*.md              @jambione/obrien

# Session journals → guinan
knowledge_base/sessions/                              @jambione/guinan

# Governance → picard
knowledge_base/documents/knowledge-base-governance.md @jambione
knowledge_base/documents/team-conventions.md          @jambione
knowledge_base/documents/past-lessons-learned.md      @jambione/guinan
knowledge_base/documents/agent-performance-log.md     @jambione
